com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services

Interface SupplierActivityTaskService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultSupplierActivityTaskService

    public interface SupplierActivityTaskService

    This communication scenario enables a remote system to read supplier activity task from the SAP S/4HANA tenant. The remote system calls the synchronous OData service API_SUPPLIER_ACTIVITY_TASK. Authentication is performed using the user name/password or X.509 certificate.

    Business Documentation

    Reference: SAP API Business Hub

    Details:

    OData Service:API_SUPPLIER_ACTIVITY_TASK_SRV
    API Version:1
    Minimum ERP Version:1708
    Communication Scenario:Supplier Activity Task Integration (SAP_COM_0138)
    Scope Items:Business Partner for Treasury and Risk Management (19C)
